Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了  絹江
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  此人在200年前就已死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being出現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力干涉原斯里蘭卡的內部紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向雙方展開了攻擊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向雙方展開了攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做明明只會使雙方的感情進一步惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being  到底在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的以為靠一次軍事介入就能結束持續了300多年的紛爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只一次  會一直介入的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至紛爭結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至憎恨指向我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是伴隨改變事物的疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會被幹掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是首次介入紛爭  他有自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他會是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合的運輸機？  在這個空域？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Flag嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:21:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆·艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的存在奪走了內心的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能接受連對話都要拒絕的行為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對擺在眼前的刀刃  少年感受到了時代的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「變化的世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是無法指定的現實


